* Dead Tree: https://www.amazon.com/dp/1491910399/

### Club 2
* Title: Feature Engineering and Selection
* Online: http://www.feat.engineering/
* Dead Tree: https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/1138079227/

### Club 3
