* Online: http://appliedpredictivemodeling.com/
* Dead Tree: https://www.amazon.com/dp/B00K15TZU0/

### Club 4
* Title: Advanced R
* Online: https://adv-r.hadley.nz/
* Dead Tree: https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/0815384572

